{"tid":2416532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★市建局：「健康碼」連結「安心出行」直接與確診個案大廈資料庫連結！！","createTime":"2021-02-21T06:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T13:52:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b1511387b113b5dbe7a7b2b1da6ad2b219b20b64","tid":2416532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:47:13.000Z","msg":"市建局行政總監韋志成表示，市建局去年10月曾在重建項目的凍結人口調查中，應用自行研發的「健康碼」感染風險提示程式，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>本月中再推出加強功能的「健康碼」2.0版本，稍後會率先使用於收地調查。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n韋志成在網誌說，首個版本程式未能準確記錄室內位置，<span class=\"xx-large\">新版本加入掃瞄「安心出行」場地二維碼的功能，並直接與當局的確診個案大廈資料庫連結</span>，以便職員預早計劃行程，避免走近高風險區域。他說，市建局團隊十分明白職員重視私隱，新版程式將所有定位記錄改為儲存在職員的個人手機內，減低職員對私隱外洩的擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576654-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576654-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvndg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=860f19e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576654-20210221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=04071e25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576654-20210221.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"67a4105f2ab0e0b984e5ac4487116234f563f05c","tid":2416532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e3da46a91d3a5184aece9be55ac34c3b32f7b8","tid":2416532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":